00:42:13.780 --> 00:42:14.640
Maggagabi na.

00:42:15.140 --> 00:42:16.200
Kain na tayong lahat.

00:42:18.140 --> 00:42:19.180
Lola ni Xiguang, dapat ka ring sumama.

00:42:21.540 --> 00:42:23.320
Mag-isa lang sa bahay ang lolo ni Guang,

00:42:23.600 --> 00:42:24.920
kaya dapat na siguro akong bumalik.

00:42:31.320 --> 00:42:32.000
Sige, kung ganoon.

00:42:33.480 --> 00:42:34.680
Lola, kumusta ang pag-uwi mo?

00:42:35.040 --> 00:42:36.040
May nakahanda nang sakay para sa akin.

00:42:37.300 --> 00:42:38.300
Ihahatid na lang kita papunta sa kotse kung ganoon.

00:42:46.400 --> 00:42:46.860
Mag-ingat.

00:42:46.940 --> 00:42:47.200
Gagawin ko.

00:42:54.600 --> 00:42:55.520
Lin,

00:42:56.780 --> 00:42:58.180
kapag natapos na ang lahat ng kaguluhang ito,

00:42:59.460 --> 00:43:00.700
Dapat pumunta kayo ni Guang dito

00:43:00.720 --> 00:43:01.680
papunta sa aming lugar.

00:43:02.580 --> 00:43:04.180
Ipagluluto kita ng espesyal.

00:43:05.360 --> 00:43:05.620
Gusto ko sanang gawin.

00:43:06.260 --> 00:43:07.900
Siguradong madalas akong bibisita.

00:43:10.040 --> 00:43:11.180
Aalis na ako kung ganoon.

00:43:12.940 --> 00:43:13.560
Umuwi nang ligtas.

00:43:32.440 --> 00:43:33.500
Magkain tayo ng simpleng kainan.

00:43:35.300 --> 00:43:35.900
Ikaw ay naging

00:43:36.100 --> 00:43:37.280
tumatakbo pabalik-balik
at tiyak na pagod na pagod.

00:43:37.660 --> 00:43:38.580
Kapag natapos na tayo,

00:43:39.040 --> 00:43:40.280
magpalipas lang ng gabi sa bahay

00:43:40.600 --> 00:43:41.360
at huwag nang bumalik sa Suzhou.

00:43:42.680 --> 00:43:43.300
Ikaw rin, Lin.

00:43:43.920 --> 00:43:44.560
Huwag kang mag-alala tungkol sa pagmamaneho.

